{"tid":2076937,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"脫襲警罪 大專生泛淚 「宵禁半年終可出夜街」","createTime":"2020-06-24T02:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T02:52:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da139396418770aaa01199b943504f18ba3bc5dd","tid":2076937,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/4J2POWVTLOHBHYU7GFJZUST25U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F4J2POWVTLOHBHYU7GFJZUST25U%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=e1e25716\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F4J2POWVTLOHBHYU7GFJZUST25U%2F&h=cff03878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/4J2POWVTLOHBHYU7GFJZUST25U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n脫襲警罪 大專生泛淚<br />\n「宵禁半年終可出夜街」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年12月沙田警民衝突，一名大專男生被指高舉相機上前並踢警長，經審訊後昨獲裁定襲警罪不成立。裁判官李志豪裁決時直言，曾數次仔細翻看案發影片，均沒發現與男生外形相若的人，認為稱目睹男生施襲的警員觀察有誤。男生獲悉脫罪後眼泛淚光，坦言鬆一口氣，在庭外勸勉香港人：「繼續加油，唔好放棄！」他又在法院外舉起「五大訴求、缺一不可」手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RZJN2BNYGX6ABCX5BEXDYIVXPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRZJN2BNYGX6ABCX5BEXDYIVXPU.jpg&h=626e700e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告洪嘉榮脫罪後在庭外舉起「五大訴求」手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n髮色易識別 片段證無辜<br />\n<br />\n在知專就讀的被告洪嘉榮（20歲）被控去年12月15日在沙田港鐵站襲擊警長陳勁濤。他聞判眼泛淚光，散庭後立即走到旁聽席與女友相擁，並與聲援者輪流握手及擁抱，感謝支持。有聲援者叮囑他：「食多啲嘢，肥啲！」洪表示，雖然事先知道勝算頗高，但心情難免緊張，聞判後終可鬆口氣，他指經過長達半年的宵禁後，「終於可以出夜街」。他又特別感謝家人及女友一直默默支持。<br />\n<br />\n李官昨裁決時指，。。。。。，故裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n陳早前供稱，。。。。。。但吳看過案發影片後，坦承看不見被告。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC4500/1<br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n又濫捕鳩告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9"},{"pid":"953d584ba615d8c2b12d436fe0f9d9e243fbe8a9","tid":2076937,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26dd57226073c45c5ee3dd8b9bd0c863b1044089","tid":2076937,"uid":15954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"明知告唔入都要浪費納稅人錢"},{"pid":"29bc0a8efedec14dad8cf832c8832b40a248b044","tid":2076937,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"以黑警既脆弱程度黎講就算係空氣都可以對佢做成傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc98b36fd3a858ad80d8c9780fdc16367f9d67c","tid":2076937,"uid":146737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=b64689d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"42f16d871e3d83d9b25f729efbd8fb5bb5a68954","tid":2076937,"uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"咁多case都係唔夠證據入, 姐係黑警唔可信啦<br />\n會唔會影響d官之後判決??"}]}